## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tirzepatide Zepbound 2024 SURMOUNT-OSA** = first FDA-approved drug for obstructive sleep apnea — paradigm shift after 40+ years of CPAP-only era. GLP-1 + GIP dual agonist mechanism via weight loss + 만성 metabolic. quantum-VQE 의 GLP-1R + GIPR dual pocket fit.
2. **Inspire HNS 2014** = first FDA implantable hypoglossal nerve stimulator — moderate-severe OSA CPAP-intolerant. non-drug device 의 paradigm. Genio (Nyxoah) bilateral leadless 가 second-gen pending.
3. **AD036 (Apnimed atomoxetine + aroxybutynin) Phase 3** = first oral OSA drug candidate via NRI + M3R upper airway dilator tone. 2024-2025 readout 임박. quantum-VQE 의 dual-target combination scaffold fit.
4. **solriamfetol Sunosi 2019 + pitolisant Wakix 2019** = residual EDS in CPAP-treated OSA — wake-promoting paradigm 확장. modafinil 2003 OSA-EDS 의 next-gen alternative.
5. **acetazolamide CSA + high-altitude AMS** = carbonic anhydrase inhibition으로 central respiratory drive 자극. classical drug 인데 CSA + AMS 적응증 양립 (cross-climate_health).
6. **CPAP since Sullivan 1981** = 40+ years OSA 표준 — auto-CPAP / BiPAP / ASV 가 generational evolution. compliance < 50% 가 임상 한계 → drug + HNS 가 alternative.
7. **OHS (obesity hypoventilation syndrome)** = pulmonology + obesity + sleep medicine cross-domain. BMI ≥ 30 + PaCO2 > 45 awake. NIV + weight loss + tirzepatide 가 만성 disease-modifying.
8. **cardiovascular outcome (afib + HF + stroke + 만성)** = OSA 치료 가 CV outcome 개선 evidence — SAVE trial 이 negative 였으나 SERVE-HF 가 ASV CSA-HF subgroup 에서 mortality 증가 — ASV 사용 제한 (만성 cross-cardiology).
9. **K-OSA 산정특례 framework** = 한국 healthcare 에서 OSA + CPAP 보험 framework 2018+ 시행. 식약처 OSA drug pipeline 가 tirzepatide (2024) 후 broader (cross-k_pharma_industry).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, sleep apnea specific 임상 의미 한정.

